data.description: Impressive 3,377 sq ft 1 level updated home located in the community of Pinnacle County Club.  The foyer welcomes you to an open floor plan that is ideal for entertaining featuring open Living Room & Dining Room with private Study & Kitchen with quartz waterfall center island, large pantry, & breakfast room. The primary suite retreat has a tray ceiling, & lavish master bath with jetted bathtub, walk-in shower and 2 walk-in closets. Home boasts 2 additional guest bedrooms & bonus/recreation space. Newly added pool house features a luxury chef’s kitchen featuring top-of-the-line appliances, a large center island, elegant quartz countertops, floor to ceiling cabinetry & full pool bathroom all with views of the backyard. The backyard is a private oasis both relaxing & entertaining featuring a covered patio with vaulted wooden ceiling & dining space, double sided fireplace & outdoor kitchen all overlooking a stunning European style pool with electric safety cover & waterfall. Home also features a large four-car garage.
